```c
if (obj->control_type == CT_AI && result[22] > 0)
    Ai_local_info[objnum].retry_count = result[22];
```

But in the C-only path (line 1450-1452):
```c
if (obj->control_type == CT_AI) {
    if (count > 0) {
        Ai_local_info[objnum].retry_count = count-1;
